{"tid":48252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"當面被搶電話　佛山漢使「無影腳」勇擒賊匪","createTime":"2016-12-21T03:11:24.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-26T15:36:45.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8fac7a0dcef10f588095bb596d67e5d045c08749","tid":48252,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T03:11:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20161220/bkncn-20161220122713030-1220_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161220%2Fbkncn-20161220122713030-1220_05011_001.html&d=y%2BZDlISUvbTxSxmXlt41VXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=3bfcc48d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20161220/bkncn-20161220122713030-1220_05011_001.html</a> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/g1hzu6kq\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fg1hzu6kq&h=81015c36&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=y%2BZDlISUvbTxSxmXlt41VXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=982e3cc4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】 廣東佛山一名霍姓貨車司機，兩個月內在同一地方兩度被搶去電話，前日賊匪第三次光顧，從他手上搶走電話後騎電單車逃逸。霍先生之後見賊匪在對面駛過，遂隨即上前攔截，使出「無影腳」正面踢向賊匪的電單車致其翻側倒地，成功取回電話<br />\n<br />\n由於霍先生經常要開夜車，趕在早上7時前將貨物送到二手車市場，在等候貨主其間，不時在車上小睡片刻。惟之前在市場外被賊匪趁機開車門搶走手機，因此近日他將車門及車窗鎖上，以防賊匪再度光顧。未料，賊匪今次竟然敲車窗叫醒他，並自稱是貨主，要求他致電給聯絡人。當霍男接通電話後，賊匪竟伸手搶走其手機，然後騎電單車離去。 <br />\n<br />\n在霍先生不知所措之際，竟發現賊匪騎電單車從對面行車線駛過。霍先生見機不可失，隨即上前攔截，當電單車正高速迎面駛近時，霍先生朝着電單車飛踢，將賊匪連人帶車踢跌後，立即從對方手上取回手機。 <br />\n<br />\n事後，霍先生手腳有輕微擦傷，但電話失而復得已為他免去不少麻煩。他又指，二手市場附近經常發生同類型事件，希望警方能加強巡邏。"},{"pid":"9e3343e13a4bebd48ae317857af475f6ebf2e952","tid":48252,"uid":18320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T03:13:01.000Z","msg":"屌你老母留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7abfb40c95f4d0d3000b9113e545336047f0241","tid":48252,"uid":3685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T03:20:29.000Z","msg":"支那嘅野 關我撚事咩 屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"637f6156aeac2de987ea0c5eded382b9f6bb7ff5","tid":48252,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T03:26:04.000Z","msg":"唔係隔離踢過去好啲咩<br />\n雖然可能踢唔跌佢<br />\n<br />\n但係正面踢 如果條友唔係減一減速 佢就食晒啲衝擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申鳩估"},{"pid":"7d4190ba0d4dd14e60eb9ff72106b80b27f18100","tid":48252,"uid":33645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T03:35:14.000Z","msg":"自己人內哄日日有無數. 不應列作新聞"},{"pid":"d4fafe81da1698fe67836cce6255d0329ee1566f","tid":48252,"uid":20619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T03:57:01.000Z","msg":"真係佛山無影腳"},{"pid":"5224618ddb5c3f00e34dc9eee22ccc857aa25f98","tid":48252,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T05:58:05.000Z","msg":"霍元甲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"765d162fb4cd55cbbde00a3bb8f450890c0b09c9","tid":48252,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T07:37:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a0e19bd8faf3971d46b5146b512e0e5bb1f6fcf3","tid":48252,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T14:51:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4823f1d728809d58ea5af0bc82df397d12923725","tid":48252,"uid":529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T14:56:42.000Z","msg":"柒佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afb55872a7b2750951834a2cef409852f2f5fa77","tid":48252,"uid":25350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T15:36:45.000Z","msg":"支那一條街有咁撚多CCTV ，一單咁嘢都可以有多角度鏡頭剪輯條片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}